<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yī shuāng yǎn dān dān yǎng wàng zhǔ, yī kē xīn wán quán shǔ yú zhǔ.
 yī shuāng shǒu yīn qín fú shì zhǔ, yī shuāng jiǎo jǐn jǐn gēn suí zhǔ.
 zhǔ a zhè shì wǒ de xīn shēng, duō shǎo gè rì rì yè yè, zài wǒ de xīn zhōng gǎn dòng.
 yīn wèi xiàn zài huó zhe de bù zài shì wǒ, nǎi shì jī dū cì gěi wǒ yī gè xīn shēng mìng.
 nǎi shì jī dū cì gěi wǒ yī gè xīn shēng mìng.</lyrics>
